show.sharing_text_v2:
हेलो! मैंने कुकू एफएम पर इस शो को सुना और मेरे ख्‍याल से आपको भी पसंद आएगा

show.description: Bellway Zouch shared three tender years with Eason Gold, but their love was never truly equal. When she discovers she was only a stand-in for Eason’s first love, Celine Moody, Bellway makes the painful choice to leave for a new life abroad. Honoring her mother’s request, she gives herself one final month to let go. In that quiet farewell, she rediscovers her worth, heals her heart, and prepares to move on. But on the very day she leaves, Eason awakens to a devastating truth the only woman he ever truly loved was the one he let go.
